Package insa.h4401.utils

Provides the classes necessary to use generic tools The tools inside the Utils package can be used by all others classes of the projects.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IGraph
    Inteface representing a graph which can be used by generic algorithms.
    ITSP
    Interface with the methods to use to resolve the Travelling Salesman Problem.
    Publisher
    This interface describes a Publisher object, or "data" in the model-view paradigm.
    Subscriber
    A class can implement the Subscriber interface when it wants to be informed of changes in Publisher objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultTSP
    Abstract class implementing the ITSP interface.
    DocumentFactory
    This class is a factory used to build objects providing convenient interfaces to interact with input/output files used by the application
    MapDocument
    This class provides a convenient interface to extract information from the XML description of a Map
    PlanningDocument
    This class provides a convenient interface to extract information from the XML description of a Planning
    RouteDocument
    This class provides a convenient interface to write a Route output file
    TypeWrapper
    This class provides type conversion static methods
    XMLParser
    This class provides a generic XML parser.

Package insa.h4401.utils Description

Provides the classes necessary to use generic tools

The tools inside the Utils package can be used by all others classes of the projects.
